# Split - Configurações (RT1-St / SW1-St)

## Parte 2 - Clear Configs and reload equipment (Router e Switch)

### Router(RT1-St)
enable
erase startup-config (enter)
reload (no save)

### Switch(Sw1-St)  
enable
erase startup-config (enter)
delete flash:vlan.dat (enter enter)
reload (no save)

- check SDM
enable
show sdm prefer

- if necessary 
configure terminal
sdm prefer dual-ipv4-and-ipv6 default
end
copy running-config startup-config (ou simplesmente yes no reload)
reload (no save)

## Parte 3 -  Perform Equipment Initial Configuration

### Router (RT1-St) e Switch (SW1-St)

enable
configure terminal
no ip domain-lookup
hostname SW1-St
ip domain-name isepacademy.ccna.itn.com
security passwords min-length 10 (no switch não dá)
service password-encryption
enable secret classclass
username cisco privilege 15 secret classclass

crypto key generate rsa
2048

ip ssh version 2
line console 0
 password classclass
 login
exit
line vty 0 15
 transport input ssh
 login local
 exec-timeout 0 30
exit

login block-for 300 attempts 3 within 120  (no switch não dá)

banner motd #
AVISO: Acesso restrito a pessoal autorizado.
Todas as tentativas de acesso sao registadas e monitorizadas.
#

ip host RT1-Zg 172.20.7.97
ip host RT1-Pl 10.0.0.2
ip host RT1-St 10.0.0.6
ip host MLS1-Zg 172.20.7.98
ip host MLS2-Zg 172.20.7.102
ip host SW1-Zg 172.20.7.4
ip host SW2-Zg 172.20.7.5
ip host SW1-Pl 172.20.11.106
ip host SW1-St 172.20.13.234

end
copy running-config startup-config


## Parte 5 -  Configure VLANs, Trunks and Access Ports (Switch)

###Switch(SW1-St)

#### a. Criar Vlan


enable
configure terminal
vlan 5
 name APs
vlan 6
 name MANAGEMENT
vlan 7
 name NATIVE
vlan 10
 name SERVERS
vlan 20
 name ADMINISTRATION
vlan 30
 name STAFF
vlan 40
 name VOIP
vlan 50
 name WIRELESS
vlan 60
 name GUESTS
vlan 99
 name BLACKHOLE
exit

#### b. Configurar trunks e portas de acesso
-RT1-St
interface FastEthernet0/1
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 7
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 5,6,30,50,60
 switchport nonegotiate
 no shutdown
exit

- PCD
interface range FastEthernet0/2 - 15
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 30
 switchport nonegotiate
exit

- Ap1-St
interface range FastEthernet0/21 - 22
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk native vlan 5
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 5,50,60
 switchport nonegotiate
 no shutdown
exit

- Portas não usadas - Vlan 99(blackhole) e shutdown
interface range FastEthernet0/16 - 20
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 99
 switchport nonegotiate
 shutdown
exit

interface range FastEthernet0/23 - 24
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 99
 switchport nonegotiate
 shutdown
exit

- Gravar
end
copy running-config startup-config

- Verificar
show vlan brief
show interfaces trunk
show interfaces status




